{"tid":1667274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天崎上訴仲未判？？？","createTime":"2019-10-21T11:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T14:15:01.000Z","uid":273304,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9617e790017de855e33a4fd86840a34500102a90","tid":1667274,"uid":273304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"From 9/10/2019 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦一方早前陳詞指，本民前成員當晚的原意為小販爭取權益，法庭不應完全不考慮此動機。法官聽取各方陳詞後，決定押後頒布書面裁決。<br />\n<br />\n究竟個仆街政府要拖幾耐？"},{"pid":"86fb817d8f8b05eb8c3c16074eb541990e8df74d","tid":1667274,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"押後 後到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971a0ceb23e6a9a2dd74d11bc48ffd8b72d4170d","tid":1667274,"uid":13000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"4個星期內 （10/9計起）<br />\n<br />\n出書面裁決"},{"pid":"27529a08ee1f848ff02b2ec3ba616d2dab27a5bf","tid":1667274,"uid":61422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"琦"},{"pid":"2d63bc6d2c6aced56181cddd01b75706c057102d","tid":1667274,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}